        <Parent_String>combined footings [300111264], footings [300000931], spread footing components [300078751], spread footings [300078480], foundations (structural elements) [300000919], supporting and resisting elements [300078047], structural elements [300078048], structural elements and components for structural elements [300078046], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
